              .blog_heading
                h3 Where you come to Shoot 360.
                .home_under_line
              p
                span Why 360
              p
                | Videos are particularly suitable at telling a story, indicating an activity or swiftly moving between scenes. But, like the still image, video dictates what the viewer will see.While stills and videos control the viewer experience,
                | 360VR gives control to the viewer. It's active, not passive, so it involves viewers on a totally irreplaceable manner. What's more, instead of cropping or limiting the view, 360VR allows the viewer to gaze at everything in
                | all directions. It nearly places the viewer into a location. So, it carries an additional notch of reliability. The viewer can see what a place is really like.
          .col-sm-5
