                  img(src='user/images/advantage/1.png')
                .content_text
                  h4 Save Time and Effort:
                  p
                    | Instead of staging a arduous and tireless open house event, a 360 virtual tour remains permanently open for anyone who wants to visit. This saves you the time and resources you would otherwise spend scheduling an open house,
                    | keeping contacts and staying at the site while many who will never buy just come in to ask questions. It allows seller to filter the leads without visiting the sight physically. It also allows buyer to filter the property
                    | as per requirement without visiting physically. Its saves Time and effort for both buyer and seller.
            .col-md-6
              .advantage_section_img
