                    | view of each part of the Property 24*7
          .row
            .col-md-6.order-last.order-md-0
              .advantage_section_text
                div
                  img(src='user/images/advantage/3.png')
                .content_text
                  h4 Increase Conversion Ratio (ICR) : 
